claim.claim-text:
A pencil sharpener, characterized in that the pencil sharpener comprises:
a waste case (10) having

a mounting hole (111) defined in the waste case (10) and having an inner wall; and

multiple positioning segments (112) formed on the inner wall of the mounting hole (111);
a blade base (20) mounted in the waste case (10) and having a bottom;
a blocking chunk (30) moveably mounted on the bottom of the blade base (20) along an axial direction of the blade base (20) and having a bottom;
a blade (40) mounted securely on the blade base (20);
a rotating knob (50) mounted rotatably in the mounting hole (111) of the waste case (10) and having at least one engaging segment (532), wherein each one of the at least one engaging segment (532) selectively engaging one of the positioning segments (112) of the waste case (10); and
an adjusting shaft (60) connected securely with the rotating knob (50) and disposed on the bottom of the blocking chunk (30), wherein when the rotating knob (50) is rotated, the adjusting shaft (60) is rotated to push the blocking chunk (30) to move along the axial direction of the blade base (20).
